				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/Chi-Th%C4%83ng-B%C3%ACnh-k%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-song-ch%C6%B0-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-H5HDAzFqaki_JM2yHIB7mA">Chi Thăng Bình ký đồng song chư hữu - 之升平寄同窗諸友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-B%C3%ADch-San/author-GaA0SgEPvCmkAgLupJfzCQ">Trần Bích San</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-Nh%C6%B0-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-thu%E1%BB%B7/poem-pwttF1AVffdiUDEU6n0CPQ">Độ Như Thiết thuỷ - 渡如鐵水</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Huy/L%C3%A3o-La-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BA%A7n/poem-A_ZOLz4yUtVTd-aWQNs4xA">Lão La đại thần - 老羅大臣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Huy/author-8x96YHLVSKlfkIiQP331OQ">Tạ Đình Huy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C6%AFu-%C4%90%C3%A0m-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/Ph%E1%BB%95-khuy%E1%BA%BFn-ni%E1%BB%87m-Ph%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-Ryf4IcWuySESz8qSHRQFrA">Phổ khuyến niệm Phật kỳ 4 - 普勸念佛其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C6%AFu-%C4%90%C3%A0m-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-GOjxX3WrbeVYR50HQYCb7A">Ưu Đàm đại sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BA%A7u-k%E1%BB%B3-06/poem-8Am4w9SzhRFYVl9Ik4qtfQ">Phục sầu kỳ 06 - 復愁其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/Qu%C3%A1-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%A0m-kinh-Bao-Da-mi%E1%BA%BFu-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-ZvJ4q9wlZMmqbxCQF10PJA">Quá Tương Đàm kinh Bao Da miếu đề - 過湘潭經包耶廟題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_